Interpretation.

    mX→0mX​→0: infinite-range force, recover Newtonian gravity.

    mX≠0mX​=0: finite-range (Yukawa) modifications that regularize short-distance singularities.

    Proca structure gives a Lorentz-invariant massive mediator; if ∂μJμ=0∂μ​Jμ=0 then ∂μXμ=0∂μ​Xμ=0 (consistency condition).

