This Proca-like field-theoretic foundation preserves the leak/flow intuition while providing a concrete PDE framework to derive limits and predictions.

Gauge symmetry note: The mass term mXmX​ breaks the U(1)U(1) gauge symmetry, making the longitudinal mode physical and ensuring the conservation law ∂μJμ=0∂μ​Jμ=0 implies ∂μXμ=0∂μ​Xμ=0 as a dynamical constraint rather than a gauge choice.
